Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:41.15,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:396930,401150}This is the ball you won the last All-Japan championships with.{NOTE:このボールは君達が日本選手権に優勝した記念のゴールだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.15,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:401150,403150}Hold on to this and make it your mascot.{NOTE:マスコットとして持ってきたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:50.07,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:405110,410070}That ball holds the courage and memories\Nof Fujimi Academy's volleyball team.{NOTE:あのボールには富士見学園のチームメートの励ましの心がこもっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:51.91,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:410070,411910}Miss Ayuhara!{NOTE:ミス鮎原！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:53.87,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:412740,413870}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.20,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:413870,416200}I lost Johnny.{NOTE:ジョニーに逃げられてしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:416200,419500}Thank you for going out of your way to help me.{NOTE:有難う。あなたにすっかり心配かけちゃって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.83,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:419500,421830}No problem. It is something very important to you, after all.{NOTE:いいえ。大切なボールですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.79,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:421830,423790}I will surely get it back later.{NOTE:後できっと取り戻してあげる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.30,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:423790,426300}But for now I'll walk you back. Everyone must be worried.{NOTE:皆が心配しているでしょ。送っていくわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:426300,427710}Thanks.{NOTE:有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.22,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:432220,433220}Tsk.{NOTE:チェ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:434180,435890}But I'm really surprised.{NOTE:私ビックリしたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:20.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:435890,440100}If Johnny wants a ball so much,\NI can give him any other volleyball.{NOTE:ジョニーがそんなにボールが欲しいんだったら代わりの新しいボールをあげるのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.94,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:441810,443940}Ayuhara! You'd just give him another volleyball?{NOTE:鮎原！代わりのボールですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:24.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:443940,444770}Yes.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:444770,447980}But the ball he took is our lucky charm.{NOTE:ただあのボールだけは私達の勝利の守り神ですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:28.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:447980,448650}That's why—{NOTE:だから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.99,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:448650,449990}Stop right there, Miss Ayuhara.{NOTE:止めてミス鮎原！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:449990,451070}Virginia!?{NOTE:バージニア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:35.91,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:452070,455910}He steals your ball and yet\Nyou'd just give him "another one"?{NOTE:ボールを盗まれても寛大な気持ちで代わりの新しいボールをくれる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.20,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:455910,458200}It's like you're running a charity.{NOTE:丸で慈善かきどりね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.54,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:458200,459540}Boy, that must feel good.{NOTE:いい気持ちでしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:42.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:459540,462330}That's not it! I was only thinking of Johnny—{NOTE:そんな。私はただジョニーのために…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.54,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:462330,463540}Save it.{NOTE:止めて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:48.42,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:463540,468420}Even if you really feel that way,\Nwe refuse to be pitied.{NOTE:例えあなたの真心からそう言ってくれたとしても恵んでもらうのはお断りよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:50.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:468420,470050}I don't understand, Virginia!{NOTE:バージニア、酷いわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:54.59,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:470050,474590}It's just… when a rich person gives something to the poor for no reason…{NOTE:だって豊かな人が理由もなく貧しい者に何かをくれる時…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.68,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:474590,476680}…it can't be called anything but pity.{NOTE:…私達は恵んでもらったと言うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:04.06,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:480140,484060}I will bring the ball Johnny stole to your hotel tomorrow morning.{NOTE:ジョニーが盗んだボールを明日の朝までに必ずあなたのホテルに届けます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:485520,487153}Virginia! Virginia!{NOTE:バージニア！バージニア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:489820,491570}"Like running a charity"…?{NOTE:慈善かきどりだなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:15.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:491570,495570}But I just thought Johnny would be happy\Nif he could have another ball.{NOTE:私はただボールをあげればジョニーが喜ぶと思っただけなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:21.79,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:496830,501790}I suppose my selfish excuse for kindness hurt her pride.{NOTE:でも私の勝手な親切心が彼女のプライド傷つけてしまったんだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.42,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:504870,507420}I'm sorry, Virginia.{NOTE:がめんなさい、バージニア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:507420,510590}I guess even the poor have their pride as human beings.{NOTE:貧しくても人間としての誇りに生きている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:33.88,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:510590,513880}How could I forget something so important?{NOTE:私は大切なことを忘れようとしていたんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.55,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:513880,516550}I have to apologize to her tomorrow.{NOTE:明日謝らなければ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.81,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:519560,522810}This is America, the world's most civilized country.{NOTE:これが世界のトップを行く文明国アメリカ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.94,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:525980,527940}What's wrong, Kozue?{NOTE:こずえ、どうしたのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.65,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:527940,530650}You look like country bumpkin, gawking outside window like that.{NOTE:今頃になってお上りさんみたいに見つめてるなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:532110,534820}I can't believe it.{NOTE:何だか信じられないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:57.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:534820,537530}Behind such a wonderful illumination…{NOTE:こんなにも素敵なイルミネーションの裏側に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:537530,540790}…live people like Virginia.{NOTE:…バージニア達が住んでるってことが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:05.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:540790,545080}Oh, this is about you getting lost downtown again?{NOTE:あ、さっき迷い込んだっと言うダウンタウンのことね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:09.04,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:545080,549040}That was just a slum's area. Japan has those too.{NOTE:だってスラム街みたいなところなら日本にだってあるじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.46,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:549040,550460}Heh. What's so surprising about—{NOTE:フン。何よ今更。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:550460,551380}Midori!{NOTE:みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.09,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:552170,553090}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:553090,555550}Of course I know we have those too.{NOTE:もちろんあるってことは知ってたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.34,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:555550,558340}But I've never seen one in person.{NOTE:でもこの目で確かめたことがなかったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:558340,559430}Oh.{NOTE:う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:19.93,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:559430,559930}I see.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:24.48,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:559930,564480}I saw it for the first time when I met Virginia.{NOTE:私バージニアにあったことで初めてそのことが分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:28.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:564480,568900}I've only been thinking about volleyball up until now.{NOTE:私は今までバレーの事以外に何も考えたことがなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:38.82,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:574320,578820}We won against the U.S. team\Nand now South Korea.{NOTE:今日までアメリカ韓国と順調に勝ち進んできた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.99,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:578820,581990}And we'll play against Romania tomorrow.\NWhich is going to be easy.{NOTE:明日はルーマニアとの対戦だが、これは勝てる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.50,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:584120,586500}We're the superior team,\Nin both power and technique.{NOTE:力も技術もこっちが一枚上だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.50,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:586500,589500}However, the problem is how we plan to achieve our victory.{NOTE:しかし、勝ち方が問題だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:50.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:589500,590960}How we win?{NOTE:勝ち方？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.51,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:590960,593510}Let me say it clearly. Our goal is the Soviet Union.{NOTE:はっきり言おう。目指すのはソ連だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:59.26,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:595920,599260}Borchinskaya's killer spike and iron curtain-like blocking.{NOTE:ボルチンスカヤの殺人スパイクと鉄のブロック。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.64,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:599260,601640}We have no one that can defend against it.{NOTE:あれを破った人は誰にもいないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.81,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:601640,602810}Exactly.{NOTE:その通り。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.52,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:602810,604521}I'll think of a strategy.{NOTE:その対策は考えるが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:09.27,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:604521,609270}But tomorrow, I want all of you to show how accurately you can play against Romania.{NOTE:…まず明日のルーマニア戦では神経の細いプレイをしてもらう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.19,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:609270,611190}How accurate we can play?{NOTE:神経の細かいプレー？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:15.36,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:611190,615360}The Romanian team is said to use their power first and foremost.{NOTE:ルーマニアはどちらかと言うとストレートな力のチーム。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:615360,617030}But we're going to stir that up.{NOTE:それを引っ掻き回す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:21.70,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:617030,621700}And at the same time, this can serve as rehearsal for your match against the Soviet team.{NOTE:同時にソ連チームに対抗する戦術の予行演習だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.37,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:623740,625370}Alright. That's all for today.{NOTE:よし。今日はこれまで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.62,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:625370,626626}Have a good sleep.{NOTE:ぐっすり寝ておけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:36.17,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:631500,636170}We should be friendly with the other team at\Nthe World Championships, but I still want to win.{NOTE:いくら国際親善試合だからってやっぱり優勝したいもんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.59,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:636170,638590}The Soviet team is our overall goal, after all.{NOTE:結局はソ連チームが目標ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:42.97,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:639630,642970}But we still need to come up with something.{NOTE:とすればあれだけは何としても受け止めたいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.81,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:650190,651810}Killer spike.{NOTE:殺人スパイク。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.19,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:651810,653190}We don't have much time.{NOTE:時間がないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:59.95,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:655320,659950}If you try to take on a killer spike directly,\Nit'll only knock you down.{NOTE:殺人スパイクをまともに受けようとすれば弾き飛ばされるが傷ついてしまう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.32,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:659950,662320}How…!? How can we defend against it!?{NOTE:何とか、何とか…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.78,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:663320,664780}Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.62,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:664780,666620}I can't think of anything.{NOTE:駄目だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:07.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:666620,667250}Oh?{NOTE:あ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:21.38,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:679130,681380}That speed… but more importantly, that force…{NOTE:あのスピード、それにあの力。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.76,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:682510,684760}Sharp like the killer spike.{NOTE:殺人スパイクのように鋭い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:27.35,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:684760,687350}But when Virginia called him out…{NOTE:でも、バージニアが声をかけた時…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.35,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:688390,689355}Johnny!{NOTE:ジョニー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:34.61,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:692770,694610}When he got hit on the head…{NOTE:ヘッディングをやり損なった時。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:40.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:696020,700360}The ball lost its force like a balloon as it fell.{NOTE:後ろへ飛んだボールはまるで風船のように力が無くなっていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:54.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:710160,714580}If you manage to defend against that forceful spike once, its power will drop by half.{NOTE:強い力で飛んでくるボールを一度中継すれば力が半減する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:58.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:714580,718380}So rather than trying to accept it, we should focus on defusing it.{NOTE:玉を返すのではなく、後ろへ飛ばしてもいいとしたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:722880,725640}We'll fail if we try to receive it directly.{NOTE:レシーブしようとすれば失敗するんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:09.68,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:725640,729680}But if one of us was able to relay it\Nand flip it behind themselves…{NOTE:それを中継して自分の後ろへ弾き飛ばすとしたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:16.44,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:733140,736440}The killer spike's force would be cut in half.{NOTE:きっと殺人スパイクの力は半減されるのでは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:23.28,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:739570,743280}In other words, two-stage reception that adds another receptive player.{NOTE:つまりレシーブを二度に分けてする二段レシーブ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.20,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:743280,746200}It's pretty far off from volleyball's common practices.{NOTE:バレーの常識とは掛け離れているわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.66,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:746200,747660}But there is hope.{NOTE:でも希望はあるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.70,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:747660,750700}I have to think this through and consult it with the coach.{NOTE:もうすこし考えをまとめてコーチに相談しなければ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:755000,756960}Two-stage reception.{NOTE:二段レシーブ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:41.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:756960,761670}This ray of hope was possible thanks to our mascot ball and Johnny.{NOTE:こんな望みが生まれたのもマスコットボールとジョニーのおかげだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.05,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:761670,763050}Thank you.{NOTE:有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.55,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:763050,765550}Looks like we'll get through this somehow, thanks to you.{NOTE:あなた達のおかげで何とかなりそうよ。}
Comment: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:51.64,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:771640,771640}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:05.28,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:782400,785280}– Now we have plenty of practice time.\N– Ayuhara!{NOTE:—今からだって練習時間はたっぷりね。\\N—鮎原！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:08.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:787740,788910}Virginia!{NOTE:バージニア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:788910,790498}Everyone, wait a moment.{NOTE:みんなちょっと待っててね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.37,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:790950,792370}We came to return the ball.{NOTE:ボールをお返しに来ました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:16.46,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:792370,796460}Thank you. I really am sorry for yesterday.{NOTE:有難う。昨日はあなたを傷つけてしまってごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.67,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:796460,798670}Don't worry, Ayuhara.{NOTE:気にしないで、鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.96,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:798670,800960}Now, Johnny, give the girl her ball back.{NOTE:さ、ジョニー。お前の手でボールを返すのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.72,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:805430,807720}Johnny. Apologize to her already.{NOTE:ジョニー。速く彼女に謝って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.89,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:807720,810890}And swear you will never steal again.{NOTE:そして二度と盗まないと誓うの。さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:31.97,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:810890,811970}I'm giving it back.{NOTE:返すよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.19,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:814980,817190}Go to hell!{NOTE:クソ喰らえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.31,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:818150,819310}Johnny!{NOTE:ジョニー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:820570,821900}Virginia!{NOTE:バージニア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.74,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:827110,829740}I'm sorry he made a scene.{NOTE:ごめんなさい。不愉快な思いをさせてしまって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:831160,832240}It's alright.{NOTE:いいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:54.87,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:832240,834870}Johnny can keep the ball. Consider it a gift.{NOTE:このボール改めてジョニーにプレゼントするわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:58.46,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:834870,838460}Ayuhara! You don't understand anything.{NOTE:鮎原！あなたは未だ私の気持ちが分かってないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:01.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:838460,841000}No, this time I have a good reason.{NOTE:いいえ、今度はちゃんと理由があるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:841000,842630}I wanted to give you my thanks for—{NOTE:実はお礼のつもりで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.84,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:842630,845840}No matter what the reason is,\Nyou're not doing this for Johnny's sake.{NOTE:例えどんな理由があってもそれはジョニーのためではありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:845840,847840}But Johnny wanted this ball…{NOTE:でもジョニーはこのボールを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.26,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:847840,851260}I wanted to talk to you about why Johnny stole your ball in the first place.{NOTE:ジョニーがどうしてボールを盗んだか？その理由はあなたにお話するわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:17.85,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:854310,857850}This is hardly an excuse for Johnny's theft.{NOTE:これはジョニーが盗んだことの言い訳ではありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:22.23,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:857850,862230}But Johnny's mom is sick and his dad was killed in action three years ago.{NOTE:ジョニーのママは病気。そして彼のパパ三年前に戦死しました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:28.49,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:864150,868490}His mother lives a life where she can't even afford to see a doctor.{NOTE:彼のママは医者に見てもらうことさえできない生活。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:33.16,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:868490,873160}So Johnny is trying to become a professional soccer player, to break free from his poverty.{NOTE:ジョニーはそんな生活から抜け出すためにプロのサッカー選手に成ろうとしているのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:873160,875330}A professional soccer player?{NOTE:プロのサッカー選手？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:44.67,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:881540,884670}To have any chance of experiencing\Neven a little bit of the high life…{NOTE:少しでも豊かな人間らしい暮らしをするには…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:48.59,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:884670,888590}…there is no choice for him but to become a musician or a professional sportsman.{NOTE:…ミュージシャンかプロのスポーツ選手に成るしかないのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:50.34,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:888590,890340}I understand Johnny's feelings.{NOTE:ジョニーの気持ちは分かるけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:53.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:890340,893390}But I don't approve of him thinking that sports is just a way to make a lot of money.{NOTE:…スポーツを金儲けの手段にするなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:15:01.94,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:895890,901940}Johnny saw in that white ball\Nhis only hope for a happy future.{NOTE:ジョニーにとってその白いボールが自分の幸福な将来のたったひとつの希望と見えたのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:07.74,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:901940,907740}A princess like you who only plays volleyball for fun\Ncan't possibly understand his desperation.{NOTE:そんな彼の切羽詰まった気持ちなんてお嬢さんの楽しみでバレーをやってるあなた方にはとっても。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:12.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:907740,912240}Wait. I don't just play volleyball for fun.{NOTE:待って。私はお嬢さんXXでバレーをやってるつもりはないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:15.08,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:912240,915080}Then why are you playing volleyball?{NOTE:ではあなたは何のためにバレーをやってるのですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:916410,917620}I'm playing…{NOTE:それは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:18.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:917620,918660}…to win.{NOTE:勝つために。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:21.62,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:918660,921620}Is that so? So it's for the glory of victory?{NOTE:そう？勝利の栄光のために。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:24.25,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:921620,924250}How showy, for celebrations and people's praise.{NOTE:華やかな(XX・かんせい)と人々の賞賛。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.21,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:924250,925210}Hahaha.{NOTE:はははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:925210,926750}What's so funny?{NOTE:何が可笑しいの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:30.05,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:926750,930050}Sports are there for money.{NOTE:スポーツはお金儲けのためにあるものよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:34.80,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:930050,934800}But for the glory of victory…?\NGlory won't pay for a single piece of bread!{NOTE:勝利の栄光なんて。栄光なんてひとかけらのパンほどの値打ちもないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:35.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:934800,935970}Virginia!{NOTE:バージニア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.85,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:937520,938850}People are waiting for you.{NOTE:みんなが待ってる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.39,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:938850,940390}See you.{NOTE:じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:41.73,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:940390,941730}Captain, hurry up!{NOTE:キャプテン！速く！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.27,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:941730,943270}– What are you doing?\N– What's taking you so long?{NOTE:—なにしってんの？\\N—なにやってんの！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.27,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:943270,944270}Come on!{NOTE:はいよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.34,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:965500,967340}Ayuhara-san, you're great today!{NOTE:鮎原さん、さえてるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:967340,968630}We haven't even started yet.{NOTE:まだまだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.97,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:972720,974970}A princess only playing for fun.{NOTE:お嬢さんの楽しみのバレーなんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.76,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:975890,977760}Princess only playing for fun.{NOTE:お嬢さんのお楽しみ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:18.56,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:977760,978560}Victory.{NOTE:勝利。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:19.31,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:978560,979310}Glory.{NOTE:栄光。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.48,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:979310,980480}Showy celebrations.{NOTE:華やかな(XXX・かんせい)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:21.68,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:980480,981680}People's praise.{NOTE:人々賞賛。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.64,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:981680,983640}Hahaha.{NOTE:はははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:24.77,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:983640,984770}I can't believe it.{NOTE:信じられないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:27.73,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:984770,987730}The glory of victory isn't worth a single piece of bread…{NOTE:勝利の栄光はひとかけらのパンほどの値打ちもないなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.69,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:987730,988690}Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.07,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:989820,991070}It hurts.{NOTE:痛い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.95,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:991070,992950}What amazing power.{NOTE:すごい力だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:997330,998700}Kakinouchi-san.{NOTE:垣之内さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.41,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:998700,1000410}Oh, Captain. Wanna play?{NOTE:あ、キャプテン。XXX？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:41.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000410,1001660}What are we going to do?{NOTE:何やるつもりなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.17,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002790,1005170}Practice receiving killer spikes.{NOTE:殺人スパイクのレシーブの練習よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005170,1006540}Killer spikes?{NOTE:殺人スパイク？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:47.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006540,1007880}But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:52.67,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007880,1012670}Killer spike is all about grazing the net and hitting the receiver's chest with great power.{NOTE:殺人スパイクはネットすれすれの高さからレシーバーの胸は狙って飛んでくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:06.60,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021640,1026600}That's why we'll start with spikes from only three meters away.{NOTE:だからXXして……始め三メートルから思い切ってスパイクをする。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:10.44,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026600,1030440}Once we receive that,\Nwe'll gradually shorten the distance.{NOTE:それをレシーブ。そしてだんだん距離を縮めていけば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:13.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030440,1033950}That way we can produce power and speed similar to the killer spike.{NOTE:力とスピードは殺人スパイクXXXが作り出せる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033950,1035700}I see.{NOTE:そうなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.03,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035700,1037030}The two-stage reception…{NOTE:二段レシーブ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.03,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037030,1039030}Let's try it out right now.{NOTE:この場で実験してみよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.75,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041330,1043750}All of this for the glory of victory?{NOTE:それも勝利の栄光とやらのため。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:24.71,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043750,1044710}How worthless.{NOTE:下らない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.88,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045540,1047880}T-That's not true. That's not it!{NOTE:そ、そんな。そんな酷いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.04,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047880,1050040}Captain, what are you thinking about?{NOTE:キャプテン、何を考えているのね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:30.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050040,1050750}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:34.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050750,1054220}Ah, no, it's nothing.\NI'll try receiving. Kakinouchi-san, please.{NOTE:あ、んん、いいの。私レシーブするわ。垣之内さん打って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054220,1055170}Okay.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056430,1057760}I'm ready.{NOTE:いいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.64,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058550,1059640}Got it.{NOTE:よかろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.64,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061560,1062640}Okay?{NOTE:OK.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.10,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065850,1067100}Captain…!{NOTE:キャプテン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067100,1068940}It's all right! Let's continue!{NOTE:大丈夫！どんどん打ってみて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.99,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079570,1080990}Kozue's acting strange.{NOTE:変だわ、こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:03.20,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080990,1083200}It's like she's losing the ball on purpose.{NOTE:まるで態とXXにボールXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.31,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105680,1107310}What's up with you, Captain?{NOTE:XXXしたのね、キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.98,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107310,1108980}You're acting different than usual.{NOTE:いつもと全然違うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:31.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108980,1111110}It's nothing, don't worry about it.{NOTE:んん。心配しなくてもいいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.07,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113110,1115070}"Don't worry", she says…{NOTE:心配しないで言ったって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:36.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115070,1116650}Looks like we can pull it off.{NOTE:何とか行けそうだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:39.57,Alternative,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1116650,1119570}– We might stand a chance against the S—\N– Hahaha!{NOTE:—上手くすれば、これでソ連に—\\N—ははははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.53,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120820,1122530}You win and then what?{NOTE:そして勝ってどうするの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.83,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122530,1124830}Sports are there for money.{NOTE:スポーツはお金儲けのためのものよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:49.04,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124830,1129040}The glory of victory won't buy you a single piece of bread.{NOTE:勝利の栄光なんて。ひとかけらのパンほどの値打ちもないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.38,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129040,1131380}Nice social status, you little princess playing for fun.{NOTE:いいご身分ね。お嬢様のお楽しみ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.50,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131380,1132500}For fun!{NOTE:お楽しみ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:55.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132500,1135960}Is that who I am?\NI don't understand anything anymore.{NOTE:そうかしら？何だか分からなくなってきたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:57.38,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135960,1137380}Huh?{NOTE:あ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.47,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139880,1141470}No.{NOTE:いいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.51,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141470,1143510}This holds a different value than bread.{NOTE:パンとは違う値打ちがあるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:07.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143510,1147060}Putting up such a fight\Nwas all for the glory of victory.{NOTE:こうして戦うことでこれまでも勝利の栄光のため。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:10.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147060,1150650}It's what I worked hard for and spilled blood for.{NOTE:ただそれだけのために血の滲むような努力を積み重ねてきたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:23.41,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160700,1163410}I've overcome one grueling obstacle after another.{NOTE:一つ一つの苦しみに打ち勝ってきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:26.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163410,1166080}That's just my way of living,\Nloving volleyball from the bottom of my heart.{NOTE:それが心からバレーを愛する私の生き方。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.83,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166080,1168830}And I want Virginia to acknowledge that.{NOTE:そのことバージニアに見てもらう必要があるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171370,1174960}This isn't the whim of some princess.\NIt's a serious battle I've invested my life in.{NOTE:お嬢さんXX何かではない。命懸けの真剣勝負を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.51,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177380,1179510}Sports aren't just for making money.{NOTE:スポーツはお金儲けも何もない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:41.30,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179510,1181300}It's a serious fight.{NOTE:ただ真剣な戦い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:45.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181300,1185010}Even though we have different circumstances,\NI need her to understand this.{NOTE:例えどんなに立場や境遇が違っても分かってもらわなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:48.43,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185010,1188430}She needs to see what volleyball means to us.{NOTE:私達が真剣に命をかけてバレーをやっていることを見てもらうんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191730,1193150}This place…{NOTE:この入場とね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.77,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193150,1195770}It's my last chance to connect with Virginia.{NOTE:私とヴァージニアの心をつなぐ最後の方法。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.32,Default,Johnny's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201530,1202320}What do you need?{NOTE:何か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:06.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202320,1206030}Please pass this onto Virginia and Johnny.{NOTE:お願い。これをバージニアとジョニーに渡してください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:06.78,Default,Johnny's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206030,1206780}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.08,Default,Johnny's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207620,1209080}Okay.{NOTE:あ、はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:13.12,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210200,1213120}This is for the best. Virginia will come for sure.{NOTE:これでいいわ。きっとバージニアは来てくれる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.38,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213120,1215380}To watch our volleyball.{NOTE:私達のバレーを見守るために。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.36,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234810,1236360}Alright, keep it up.{NOTE:よし。その調子だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.65,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236360,1237650}Keep them confused.{NOTE:決定的に引っ掻き回す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:38.40,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1237650,1238400}– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.95,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243400,1244950}She'll come. I'm sure of it.{NOTE:きっと来てくれるわ。きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247370,1248490}Alright, let's go!{NOTE:さ、行きましょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.49,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1248490,1249490}– Yeah!\N– Yeah!{NOTE:—おう！\\N—おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.59,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1306090,1307590}Yay, we won!{NOTE:わ、勝ったね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.72,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311600,1313720}So she didn't came after all…{NOTE:とうとう来なかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.56,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318440,1319560}Ayuhara!{NOTE:鮎原！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319560,1320730}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:01.98,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320730,1321980}Congratulations.{NOTE:おめでとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:05.86,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321980,1325860}I had to work at my part-time job,\Nso I couldn't make it.{NOTE:残念ながら私がアルバイトに行っていたので間に合いませんでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:07.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325860,1327110}So that's how it was?{NOTE:そうだったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:12.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330830,1332990}I wanted you to see it.{NOTE:見てほしかったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:14.79,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332990,1334790}But it didn't fully go to waste.{NOTE:でも徒ではないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:17.54,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334790,1337540}I get to keep these tickets\Nas a token to remember you by.{NOTE:これ招待券は記念に持っています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:21.09,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339790,1341090}Goodbye.{NOTE:さようなら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:22.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341090,1342840}I won't shake hands with you just yet.{NOTE:さようなら握手はしないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:24.21,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342840,1344210}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1344210,1346090}Before we do…{NOTE:その代わりに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:32.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350680,1352560}You are a volleyball player, too.{NOTE:あなたもバレーの選手。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:35.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352560,1355390}Please accept one serve from me.{NOTE:一球だけ私のサーブを受けてちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:43.27,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362400,1363270}Okay.{NOTE:Okay.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:48.40,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1367400,1368400}Come on!{NOTE:Come on!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:52.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370950,1372580}Falling leaf!{NOTE:木の葉落とす。えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:22:56.75,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375830,1376750}Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:00.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1379080,1380080}Ah…!{NOTE:あ…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:10.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389260,1390510}Attack!{NOTE:アタック！}
